&lt;p&gt;LRK is a nationally recognized design firm built around a team of architects, urban designers, planners, and interior designers. We believe that great places are created through successful collaboration and careful consideration of how these disciplines impact and respect the surrounding community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LRK is seeking a proactive, dependable, collaborative, and creative Marketing Coordinator to join our Dallas office. &amp;nbsp;This position will be part of a team responsible for creative initiatives including writing and producing proposals, presentation design, marketing collateral development, website content management, email communications, photography, social media and other activities to market the company and personnel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will possess 5+ years of proven experience as a Marketing Coordinator in the Architecture/Engineering/Construction industry or other professional service industry. Excellent written and verbal communication skills, strong organization skills, ability to work both independently and collaboratively in a team environment, ability to work under pressure of tight deadlines and handle multiple tasks simultaneously, and ability to coordinate remotely with other offices is required. Proficiency with Microsoft Office and Adobe Creative Cloud (InDesign, Photoshop, and Illustrator) is a must. Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications, Graphic Design or related field preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information on LRK, please visit www.lrk.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Equal Opportunity Employer&lt;/p&gt;

